 may  added the responsibilities for africamiddle east region as of january  and responsibilities for latin america in march  he was named vice president of pfizer in  and promoted to president of worldwide pharmaceutical operations in  he is a member of the pfizer leadership team on  december  when read took over from jeffrey kindler as pfizer’s ceo the drug firm–the world’s largest–was facing the impending patent expiration of lipitor the bestselling drug ever made and the utter failure of one of the most lavishly funded research laboratories on the planet to develop much of anything read is also a director of kimberlyclark read is now an american citizen by october  during the drug pricing firestorm forbes journalist matthew herper wrote how read with his calculating mind must get through the public’s rage over sixfigure price tags for breakthrough drugs and yet keep pfizer’s pricing power more or less intact doing so is absolutely critical  of pfizer’s revenue growth over the past three years has come from increasing prices on existing drugs according to ssr a stamford connbased consulting firm new medicines especially for cancer are selling for plus–prices that were unimaginable five years ago personal lifeedit read has a holiday home near bonita springs florida referencesedit  a b c executive profile ian c read businessweek retrieved  november    a b c d e herper matthew  november  pfizers ceo faces the drug pricing firestorm forbes retrieved  november    clark andrew may   pfizer chief’s scottish roots buried by a reluctance to plant the flag the times retrieved  september    biographical information on pfizer ceo ian read december     pfizers jeffrey kindler resigns as chief executive bbc news  december  retrieved  november    home  pfizer one of the worlds premier biopharmaceutical companies pfizer retrieved  august    ian read forbes retrieved  november    a b rushe dominic pfizers ian read slow and steady wins the day the guardian retrieved  november   ex