t in  and assumed responsibility for canada in addition to europe in  ian later became accountable for operations in both the africamiddle east region and latin america as well   ian received his bsc in chemical engineering from london university imperial college in  he earned his chartered accountants certification from the institute of chartered accountants of england and wales in    ian serves on the boards of phrma kimberlyclark and the partnership for new york city download pdf sitemap privacy policy terms  conditions rss twitter facebook youtube medium